 _______________________________________________________________________

 Mandriva Linux Security Advisory                         MDVSA-2013:240
 http://www.mandriva.com/en/support/security/
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Package : glpi
 Date    : September 25, 2013
 Affected: Business Server 1.0
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Problem Description:

 Updated glpi package fixes security vulnerabilities:
 
 Multiple security vulnerabilities due to improper sanitation of
 user input in GLPI before versions 0.83.9 (CVE-2013-2226), 0.83.91
 (CVE-2013-2225), and 0.84.2 (CVE-2013-5696).
 
 This update provides GLPI version 0.83.91, with a patch from GLPI
 0.84.2, to fix these issues.
 _______________________________________________________________________

 References:

